- Device Name: Tuya RGB e27 Bulb Zigbee
- Device Model: Zbeacon / TS0505B
- Device Description: LED RGB Zigbee Bulb dimmable
- Link to device image: https://www.aliexpress.com/item/1005010108080390.html

